Program: Omnibus
Title: Kwame Nkrumah
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lft
Last Broadcast Date: 25 February 1997
A profile of the first president of Ghana, advocate of Pan-Africanism and non-alignment, and a founding member of the Organization of African Unity. Includes an extract from an archive interview with C.R.L James.